'''埃及航空181號班機劫機事件'''，是一架原定從[[亞歷山大國際機場|亞歷山大國際機場]]飛往[[開羅國際機場|開羅國際機場]]的[[埃及航空|埃及航空]][[空中巴士A320|空中巴士A320]]班機，於途中遭到劫持，改飛向[[拉納卡國際機場|拉納卡國際機場]]的事件<ref name="BBC2">{{cite news|title='Hijacked' Egypt plane lands in Cyprus|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35915139|accessdate=2016-03-29|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2016-03-29|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108145335/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35915139|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ekathimerini">{{cite news|title=Hijacking suspected behind Egypt Air flight landing in Cyprus|url=http://www.ekathimerini.com/207398/article/ekathimerini/news/hijacking-suspected-behind-egypt-air-flight-landing-in-cyprus|accessdate=2016-03-29|work=Ekathimerini.com|date=2016-03-29|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115141/http://www.ekathimerini.com/207398/article/ekathimerini/news/hijacking-suspected-behind-egypt-air-flight-landing-in-cyprus|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dearden">{{cite news|last1=Dearden|first1=Lizzie|title=EgyptAir plane with 82 passengers on board 'hijacked'|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-plane-hijacked-lanarca-airport-cyprus-cairo-alexandria-a6957366.html|accessdate=2016-03-29|work=The Independent|date=2016-03-29|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103012/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-plane-hijacked-lanarca-airport-cyprus-cairo-alexandria-a6957366.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在劫持飞机7小时后，所有乘客和机组人员都被释放离开飞机，劫機者向警方投降最終被拘留，機上56名乘客與8名機組人員無人遇難。<ref name="BBC1" />。而后确认劫机者为埃及人賽義夫·艾爾丁·穆斯塔法（Seif Eldin Mustafa）。

== 飛機 ==
涉事飛機為一架機齡十二年的[[空中巴士|空中巴士]][[A320|A320-200]]型客機，註冊編號為SU-GCB。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-a320-2079.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-29 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206131115/https://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-a320-2079.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

